videos.headline: Tuukka Rask opts out of Stanley Cup playoffs
videos.description: Emily Kaplan breaks down Tuukka Rask's decision to opt out of the remainder of the Stanley Cup playoffs, adding that it didn't feel like playoff hockey to him with no fans present.
